import random
import networkx as nx
import copy
import constraint

%pyspark

def change_csp_after_solve_cutset(cutset, solution, csp):
    new_csp = copy.deepcopy(csp)
    remove_constraints = []
    for var in cutset:
        new_csp.remove_variable(var)
        remove_constraints = [c for c in csp.constraints if var in c]
                
    for c in remove_constraints:
        if all(v in cutset for v in c):
            continue
        var1, var2 = c
        if var2 in cutset:
            var1, var2 = var2, var1
        dom = new_csp.domains[var2]
        dom.remove(solution[var1])
        new_csp.domains.update({var2: dom})
        
    return new_csp

%pyspark

def tree_csp_sovler_with_cuset_conditioning(csp):
    solutions = []
    graph = Constraint_graph(csp)
    cutset = graph.find_smallest_cycle_cutset()
    cutset_solutions = solve_cutset(cutset, csp)
    
    for solution in cutset_solutions:
        new_csp = change_csp_after_solve_cutset(cutset, solution, csp)
        assignment = (tree_csp_solver(new_csp))
        if assignment:
            assignment.update(solution)
            return assignment
            
    return None
